<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Us</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Raleway", sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #912d2d;
            
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding-left: 25px;
            padding-right: 25px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #fafafa;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: #ffffff;

        }

        a {
            display: block;
            background-color: #26a65b;
            color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.2s ease-in-out;
        }

        a:hover {
            background-color: #1b7a40;
        }
    </style>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../style/contact.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Contact Us</h1>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns, please feel free to reach out to us on our Telegram or Twitter account.</p>
        <a href="https://mail.google.com/" target="_blank">Gmail</a>
        <a href="https://web.whatsapp.com/" target="_blank">Phone</a>
    </div>
</body>

<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-image: url("../images/web.jpg");
